&lt;DIV&gt;The real issues at this time is aggro generation comparatively with other classes who have this AA ability, who have taken dramatic strides toward tanking parity with us due to Omens launch and content, &amp;nbsp;we take a much larger hit in aggro generation than others, as well as the availability of good main hand only weapons to make the shield AA useful&amp;nbsp; for those without BBoB/Darkblade/Fleshbiter&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;7.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Improve stun from kick/slam &lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;8.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Melee Focus Effects:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; The current level of melee foci are too limited.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; There are no mage summonned melee foci, and melee foci were not retroactively placed on older gear.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; The current list of foci is also too limited in what it acheives when compared with caster foci.&amp;nbsp;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt; &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;9.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Please add the "2 hand bash" AA skill to warriors.&amp;nbsp; It doesnt' make a whole lot of sense to be 'The Masters of Weapons" and not be able to do something with our weapons that othrs can do.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0033ff&gt;(NEW)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;10.&amp;nbsp; Increase the pushback on "Press the Attack" and the chance to interrupt on it. &lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
