&lt;DIV&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; balance bash damage to the weapon &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
