&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;8.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Melee Focus Effects:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; The current level of melee foci are too limited.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; There are no mage summonned melee foci, and melee foci were not retroactively placed on older gear.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; The current list of foci is also too limited in what it acheives when compared with caster foci.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt; (NEW)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;9.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Taunt.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Success rate, particularly the steep decline vs. Yellow/Red mobs, is too low and too unreliable, and an "out of range messgae" should not result in a greyed out taunt button.&amp;nbsp;&lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt; (NEW)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;BR&gt;10.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Endurance Regen:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; We need endurance regen from Spells and/or items.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Modrods should provide an endurance benefit equal to the mana benefit.&amp;nbsp; Also, change + Endurance only augments to +Endurance regen.&amp;nbsp;&lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt; (NEW)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
